 友有没有推荐一款浏览器，最好能解决两点问题:1 、方便同步多平台书签（ Windows ，MacOs ，Android ） 2 、在 win/mac/Android 三个平台都能安装油猴插件的。</p>\n", "last_modified": 1694074352, "replies": 141, "id": 971770}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_large.png?m=1650095340", "name": "qna", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_normal.png?m=1650095340", "title": "问与答", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/qna", "topics": 210540, "footer": "", "header": "一个更好的世界需要你持续地提出好问题。", "title_alternative": "Questions and Answers", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_mini.png?m=1650095340", "stars": 3934, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 12, "parent_node_name": "v2ex"}, "member": {"id": 630352, "username": "superstarhunt", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/superstarhunt", "website": null, "twitter": null, "psn": null, "github": null, "btc": null, "location": null, "tagline": null, "bio": null, "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/0e24fa7dfa7dc91a2778c16401460cdb?s=24&d=retro", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/0e24fa7dfa7dc91a2778c16401460cdb?s=48&d=retro", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/0e24fa7dfa7dc91a2778c16401460cdb?s=73&d=retro", "created": 1684814202, "last_modified": 1684814202}, "last_reply_by": "ixx", "last_touched": 1694141889, "title": "博客园要没啦？", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/971719", "created": 1694067114, "deleted": 0, "content": "", "content_rendered": "", "last_modified": 1694067156, "replies": 116, "id": 971719}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_large.png?m=1692078075", "name": "programmer", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_normal.png?m=1692078075", "title": "程序员", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/programmer", "topics": 58719, "footer": "", "header": "While code monkeys are not eating bananas, they're coding.", "title_alternative": "Programmer", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_mini.png?m=1692078075", "stars": 8577, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 300, "parent_node_name": "computer"}, "member": {"id": 312178, "username": "hsfzxjy", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/hsfzxjy", "website": "https://i.hsfzxjy.site", "twitter": "", "psn": "", "github": "hsfzxjy", "btc": "", "location": "", "tagline": "", "bio": "", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/5c9f/e595/312178_mini.png?m=1541308309", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/5c9f/e595/312178_normal.png?m=1541308309", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/5c9f/e595/312178_large.png?m=1541308309", "created": 1524808901, "last_modified": 1541308309}, "last_reply_by": "summerLast", "last_touched": 1694097617, "title": "Github 新首页就是一坨屎", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/971693", "created": 1694063407, "deleted": 0, "content": "我不清楚这个新首页是否还在灰度测试，但看 [官方的 Discussion]( https://github.com/orgs/community/discussions/categories/feed) ，过去 12-24 小时应该有很多人受到了影响。\r\n\r\n上一个版本的 Dashboard 还是非常有用的，我在那里可以看到近期哪些人关注了我、哪些人 star/fork 了我的项目，以及我关注的人在干什么。\r\n\r\n但是在新版中，这些都没有了。取而代之的是一堆无意义的推广。尽管右上角有个煞有介事的 Filters ，但无论怎么调都调不回之前的样子。\r\n\r\n有一种被短视频平台同化了的美。", "content_rendered": "<p>我不清楚这个新首页是否还在灰度测试，但看 <a href=\"https://github.com/orgs/community/discussions/categories/feed\" rel=\"nofollow\">官方的 Discussion</a> ，过去 12-24 小时应该有很多人受到了影响。</p>\n<p>上一个版本的 Dashboard 还是非常有用的，我在那里可以看到近期哪些人关注了我、哪些人 star/fork 了我的项目，以及我关注的人在干什么。</p>\n<p>但是在新版中，这些都没有了。取而代之的是一堆无意义的推广。尽管右上角有个煞有介事的 Filters ，但无论怎么调都调不回之前的样子。</p>\n<p>有一种被短视频平台同化了的美。</p>\n", "last_modified": 1694063407, "replies": 61, "id": 971693}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_large.png?m=1692078075", "name": "programmer", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_normal.png?m=1692078075", "title": "程序员", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/programmer", "topics": 58719, "footer": "", "header": "While code monkeys are not eating bananas, they're coding.", "title_alternative": "Programmer", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_mini.png?m=1692078075", "stars": 8577, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 300, "parent_node_name": "computer"}, "member": {"id": 577956, "username": "blackyoung", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/blackyoung", "website": "", "twitter": null, "psn": null, "github": null, "btc": null, "location": "", "tagline": "", "bio": "", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/0d1ee80b966d32f17eeee98d9e86cca0?s=24&d=retro", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/0d1ee80b966d32f17eeee98d9e86cca0?s=48&d=retro", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/0d1ee80b966d32f17eeee98d9e86cca0?s=73&d=retro", "created": 1649651865, "last_modified": 1649651865}, "last_reply_by": "justfindu", "last_touched": 1694142261, "title": "在公司摸鱼写自己小项目，如何尽量安全地 push 出去？", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/971896", "created": 1694127851, "deleted": 0, "content": "有 it 的大佬帮忙解答疑惑么？如何尽量安全的在公司电脑 git push 到 GitHub ？是自己摸鱼写写小项目与公司项目完全无关。但是毕竟是摸鱼了，被查到总归不好。\r\n公司电脑有 mcafee ，应该能检测所有对外输出数据的动作？另外通过 adb push 到手机上是否安全呢？有没有懂 it 的大佬帮忙看看。有相对安全的手段就行。", "content_rendered": "<p>有 it 的大佬帮忙解答疑惑么？如何尽量安全的在公司电脑 git push 到 GitHub ？是自己摸鱼写写小项目与公司项目完全无关。但是毕竟是摸鱼了，被查到总归不好。\n公司电脑有 mcafee ，应该能检测所有对外输出数据的动作？另外通过 adb push 到手机上是否安全呢？有没有懂 it 的大佬帮忙看看。有相对安全的手段就行。</p>\n", "last_modified": 1694127851, "replies": 55, "id": 971896}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_large.png?m=1650095340", "name": "qna", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_normal.png?m=1650095340", "title": "问与答", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/qna", "topics": 210540, "footer": "", "header": "一个更好的世界需要你持续地提出好问题。", "title_alternative": "Questions and Answers", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_mini.png?m=1650095340", "stars": 3934, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 12, "parent_node_name": "v2ex"}, "member": {"id": 545546, "username": "amirobotics", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/amirobotics", "website": null, "twitter": null, "psn": null, "github": null, "btc": null, "location": null, "tagline": null, "bio": null, "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/2d9845788c3deb1bb10e698c619436b4?s=24&d=retro", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/2d9845788c3deb1bb10e698c619436b4?s=48&d=retro", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/2d9845788c3deb1bb10e698c619436b4?s=73&d=retro", "created": 1621221712, "last_modified": 1694056155}, "last_reply_by": "yuanhuaqiang", "last_touched": 1694142302, "title": "后悔在 2020 年 1 月时买了仅 8G 内存笔记本，而且还不能自行增加内存。。。", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/971661", "created": 1694056707, "deleted": 0, "content": "2019 年末，网络上铺天盖地的 AMD YES 。。。\r\n\r\n一股脑冲动，买了 AMD 处理器，1G 给了核显，剩下 7G 。在 2020 年，还够用。\r\n\r\n到了 2023 年一切都变了，\r\n - 单开个 dota2 ，内存占用率达到 90%++，\r\n - 单开 firefox ，内存也能达到 90%。。。\r\n - 开几个复杂些的 excel ，内存也能达到 90%。。。\r\n\r\n苦不堪言，开 dota2+firefox ，dota2 很大概率崩溃（尤其是团战）。。。dota2 崩溃，导致被队友举报，很无助。。。\r\n\r\n那时候花了 rmb3100 买了誉为“性价比”的笔记本，到头来，仅用了大约 2 年半。。。\r\n如果那时候花多 rmb200 买个 16G 的版本，这些问题都不复存在。\r\n\r\n哎。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。", "content_rendered": "<p>2019 年末，网络上铺天盖地的 AMD YES 。。。</p>\n<p>一股脑冲动，买了 AMD 处理器，1G 给了核显，剩下 7G 。在 2020 年，还够用。</p>\n<p>到了 2023 年一切都变了，</p>\n<ul>\n<li>单开个 dota2 ，内存占用率达到 90%++，</li>\n<li>单开 firefox ，内存也能达到 90%。。。</li>\n<li>开几个复杂些的 excel ，内存也能达到 90%。。。</li>\n</ul>\n<p>苦不堪言，开 dota2+firefox ，dota2 很大概率崩溃（尤其是团战）。。。dota2 崩溃，导致被队友举报，很无助。。。</p>\n<p>那时候花了 rmb3100 买了誉为“性价比”的笔记本，到头来，仅用了大约 2 年半。。。\n如果那时候花多 rmb200 买个 16G 的版本，这些问题都不复存在。</p>\n<p>哎。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。</p>\n", "last_modified": 1694056707, "replies": 46, "id": 971661}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_large.png?m=1692078075", "name": "programmer", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_normal.png?m=1692078075", "title": "程序员", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/programmer", "topics": 58719, "footer": "", "header": "While code monkeys are not eating bananas, they're coding.", "title_alternative": "Programmer", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_mini.png?m=1692078075", "stars": 8577, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 300, "parent_node_name": "computer"}, "member": {"id": 536311, "username": "bugmakerprox1", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/bugmakerprox1", "website": "", "twitter": null, "psn": null, "github": null, "btc": null, "location": "", "tagline": "", "bio": "", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/cb2baed52be31ecc063c2bd8cd45c82b?s=24&d=retro", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/cb2baed52be31ecc063c2bd8cd45c82b?s=48&d=retro", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/cb2baed52be31ecc063c2bd8cd45c82b?s=73&d=retro", "created": 1615022095, "last_modified": 1615022095}, "last_reply_by": "ganbuliao", "last_touched": 1694086272, "title": "近期需要大量阅读 github 开源项目，遇到一个痛点", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/971712", "created": 1694065856, "deleted": 0, "content": "近期需要大量阅读 github 开源项目，遇到一个痛点：\r\n如何在不把项目从 github 上 clone 本地的情况下，在本地编译器里面打开 github 上的项目？\r\n每一个都 git clone 到本地，然后再到 ide 里打开，感觉效率太低了", "content_rendered": "<p>近期需要大量阅读 github 开源项目，遇到一个痛点：\n如何在不把项目从 github 上 clone 本地的情况下，在本地编译器里面打开 github 上的项目？\n每一个都 git clone 到本地，然后再到 ide 里打开，感觉效率太低了</p>\n", "last_modified": 1694065856, "replies": 46, "id": 971712}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/3c59/dc04/21_large.png?m=1650127623", "name": "shenzhen", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/3c59/dc04/21_normal.png?m=1650127623", "title": "深圳", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/shenzhen", "topics": 2838, "footer": "", "header": "", "title_alternative": "Shenzhen", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/3c59/dc04/21_mini.png?m=1650127623", "stars": 1861, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 21, "parent_node_name": "cn"}, "member": {"id": 542757, "username": "xmLee", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/xmLee", "website": null, "twitter": null, "psn": null, "github": null, "btc": null, "location": null, "tagline": null, "bio": null, "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/547849b15822a447d0cbed324247a706?s=24&d=retro", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/547849b15822a447d0cbed324247a706?s=48&d=retro", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/547849b15822a447d0cbed324247a706?s=73&d=retro", "created": 1618581772, "last_modified": 1618581772}, "last_reply_by": "IDAEngine", "last_touched": 1694141970, "title": "深圳暴雨", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/971923", "created": 1694135845, "deleted": 0, "content": "v 友们放假了吗", "content_rendered": "<p>v 友们放假了吗</p>\n", "last_modified": 1694135845, "replies": 45, "id": 971923}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_large.png?m=1692078075", "name": "programmer", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_normal.png?m=1692078075", "title": "程序员", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/programmer", "topics": 58719, "footer": "", "header": "While code monkeys are not eating bananas, they're coding.", "title_alternative": "Programmer", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_mini.png?m=1692078075", "stars": 8577, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 300, "parent_node_name": "computer"}, "member": {"id": 437017, "username": "Rever4433", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/Rever4433", "website": "", "twitter": null, "psn": null, "github": null, "btc": null, "location": "", "tagline": "", "bio": "", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/c155bb592ed08e101c28e7f74174abed?s=24&d=retro", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/c155bb592ed08e101c28e7f74174abed?s=48&d=retro", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/c155bb592ed08e101c28e7f74174abed?s=73&d=retro", "created": 1566284181, "last_modified": 1566284181}, "last_reply_by": "sun4076", "last_touched": 1694120377, "title": "突发奇想，车上能不能放个闲置安卓手机记录行驶中车牌号", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/971704", "created": 1694065513, "deleted": 0, "content": "每天开车上下班，总觉得有一些车牌是我经常见过的，但仔细一想也并不清楚是在哪里见过。所以想看看有没有类似的软件来实现如下功能：\r\n1. 手机摄像头开启，支持实时识别车牌。\r\n2. 识别到车牌后记录车牌号、时间、出现的次数和当前的位置。\r\n3. 实时识别时，如果车牌出现次数>N 次，则会弹出此车牌最近出现的位置。", "content_rendered": "<p>每天开车上下班，总觉得有一些车牌是我经常见过的，但仔细一想也并不清楚是在哪里见过。所以想看看有没有类似的软件来实现如下功能：</p>\n<ol>\n<li>手机摄像头开启，支持实时识别车牌。</li>\n<li>识别到车牌后记录车牌号、时间、出现的次数和当前的位置。</li>\n<li>实时识别时，如果车牌出现次数&gt;N 次，则会弹出此车牌最近出现的位置。</li>\n</ol>\n", "last_modified": 1694065513, "replies": 41, "id": 971704}]